OL,3,CMore than 300 police officers and
OL,4,Cstaff declare Freemasons involvement
OL,6,FMore than 300 Metropolitan Police
OL,7,Fofficers and staff have declared their
OL,8,Finvolvement in the Freemasons or other
OL,9,F"hierarchical associations" after the
OL,10,Fforce required them to do so last
OL,11,Fmonth, a High Court judge has said.
OL,13,FThe Met announced in December that
OL,14,Fmembership of the Freemasons or
OL,15,Fsimilar organisations would be added
OL,16,Fto its declarable associations policy.
