OL,3,CMore than 300 police officers and
OL,4,Cstaff declare Freemasons involvement
OL,6,FThe United Grand Lodge of England
OL,7,F(UGLE), also acting on behalf of the
OL,8,FOrder of Women Freemasons (OWF) and
OL,9,Fthe Honourable Fraternity of Ancient
OL,10,FFreemasons (HFAF), said last month
OL,11,Fthat it was seeking an injunction to
OL,12,Fsuspend the policy until the outcome
OL,13,Fof the full challenge.
OL,15,FIn a court order on January 2, which
OL,16,Fwas published on Monday, Mr Justice
OL,17,FChamberlain said the issue of whether
OL,18,Fto grant an injunction would be
OL,19,Fdetermined by a judge without a
OL,20,Fhearing this week.
