OL,3,CMore than 300 police officers and
OL,4,Cstaff declare Freemasons involvement
OL,6,FHe said: "The challenged decision
OL,7,Fpurports to impose a requirement to
OL,8,Fdisclose involvement with Masonic and
OL,9,Fother associations.
OL,11,F"The requirement is applicable
OL,12,Fimmediately.
OL,14,F"It is therefore important that the
OL,15,Fquestion of interim relief be
OL,16,Fdetermined relatively quickly.
