OL,3,CMore than 300 police officers and
OL,4,Cstaff declare Freemasons involvement
OL,6,F"However, there is no pressing need
OL,7,Ffor immediate interim relief at this
OL,8,Fstage, given that some 300 officers
OL,9,Fand staff have already declared their
OL,10,Finvolvement in Masonic and other
OL,11,Fhierarchical associations."
OL,13,FMr Justice Chamberlain continued:
OL,14,F"There is no suggestion that the
OL,15,Fdefendant plans to take any
OL,16,Fdisciplinary action against any
OL,17,Fofficer or staff member for not making
OL,18,Fa declaration in the next few weeks."
