OL,6,FThe judge also said that the force had
OL,7,F"agreed to consider whether to
OL,8,Fwithdraw the challenged decision in
OL,9,Fthe light of representations" from the
OL,10,FOWF and HFAF.
OL,12,FThe Met previously said it would
OL,13,F"robustly defend" a challenge against
OL,14,Fits decision, which it said followed a
OL,15,Fsurvey of officers and staff that
OL,16,Fshowed two-thirds of respondents felt
OL,17,Fmembership of such organisations
OL,18,Faffects perception of police
OL,19,Fimpartiality and public trust.
