OL,3,CMore than 300 police officers and
OL,4,Cstaff declare Freemasons involvement
OL,6,FMore recently, Met chief Sir Mark
OL,7,FRowley has pushed the plan to declare
OL,8,Fmembership as part of wider moves to
OL,9,Fimprove transparency in the force.
OL,11,FBut the UGLE has previously said that
OL,12,Fthe reporting requirement could
OL,13,Fundermine the public credibility of
OL,14,FFreemasons and could breach their
OL,15,Fhuman rights and GDPR rules.
OL,17,FIt also claimed that less than 5% of
OL,18,Fofficers and staff completed the
OL,19,Fsurvey on the issue.
